-- Disney Names Pleasants, Pitaro Co-Heads of Disney Interactive
-- B y   D a n   H a r t
-- 2010-10-03T17:07:13Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-03/disney-names-pleasants-pitaro-co-heads-of-disney-interactive.html
Walt Disney Co. named John Pleasants
and James Pitaro co-presidents of its Disney Interactive Media
Group, the company said in a statement.  The two will run the media company’s digital games
businesses, including online, console and mobile versions, as
well as Disney’s branded and social media Web sites, the company
said in a Business Wire statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Dan Hart at 
 dahart@bloomberg.net  